# Alur Kerja: Update Code Lokal → Deploy ke Vercel

---

## Gambaran Alur

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["✏️ Edit Code\n(Lokal)"] --> B["🧪 Test Lokal\n(npm run dev)"]
    B --> C["📦 Git Commit\n& Push"]
    C --> D["🚀 Vercel\nAuto-Deploy"]
    D --> E["🌐 Live!\n(vercel.app)"]
```

> **Prinsip utama:** Setiap kali Anda `git push` ke GitHub, Vercel **otomatis** build & deploy ulang. Tidak perlu deploy manual.

---

## Step 1: Jalankan Server Lokal

Buka **2 terminal** terpisah:

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Backend API
cd "c:\Users\HYPE AMD\BELAJAR\Coding Anti gravity\apps\api"
npm run dev
# ✅ Berjalan di http://localhost:3001

# Terminal 2 — Frontend
cd "c:\Users\HYPE AMD\BELAJAR\Coding Anti gravity\apps\admin-dashboard"
npm run dev
# ✅ Berjalan di http://localhost:5174
```

Buka `http://localhost:5174` di browser untuk preview.

